#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.random.choice.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.random.choice"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.choice.choice:1 of
msgid "Generates a random sample from a given 1-D array"
msgstr "从给定的 1 维数组中生成随机样本"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.choice.choice of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.choice.choice:3 of
msgid ""
"If a tensor, a random sample is generated from its elements. If an int, "
"the random sample is generated as if a were mt.arange(a)"
msgstr ""
"如果是一个张量，则从其元素中生成随机样本。如果是一个整数，则生成的"
"随机样本如同 a 是 mt.arange(a) 一样"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.choice.choice:6 of
msgid ""
"Output shape.  If the given shape is, e.g., ``(m, n, k)``, then ``m * n *"
" k`` samples are drawn.  Default is None, in which case a single value is"
" returned."
msgstr ""
"输出形状。如果给定的形状例如为 ``(m, n, k)``，则抽取 ``m * n * k`` 个样本"
"。默认为 None，此时返回单个值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.choice.choice:10 of
msgid "Whether the sample is with or without replacement"
msgstr "样本是否有放回"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.choice.choice:12 of
msgid ""
"The probabilities associated with each entry in a. If not given the "
"sample assumes a uniform distribution over all entries in a."
msgstr ""
"与 a 中每个条目关联的概率。如果未提供，则样本在 a 的所有条目上服从"
"均匀分布。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.choice.choice:16 of
msgid "Desired chunk size on each dimension"
msgstr "每个维度上期望的块大小"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.choice.choice:18 of
msgid "Allocate the tensor on GPU if True, False as default"
msgstr "如果为 True，则在 GPU 上分配张量，默认为 False"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.choice.choice of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.choice.choice:21 of
msgid "**samples** -- The generated random samples"
msgstr "**samples** -- 生成的随机样本"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.choice.choice of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.choice.choice of
msgid "抛出"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.choice.choice:24 of
msgid ""
"If a is an int and less than zero, if a or p are not 1-dimensional,     "
"if a is an array-like of size 0, if p is not a vector of     "
"probabilities, if a and p have different lengths, or if     replace=False"
" and the sample size is greater than the population     size"
msgstr ""
"如果 a 是一个负整数，或者 a 或 p 不是一维的，或者 a 是长度为 0 的类数组"
"对象，或者 p 不是概率向量，或者 a 和 p 长度不同，或者 replace=False 但"
"样本数量大于总体数量"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.choice.choice:26 of
msgid ":py:obj:`randint`, :py:obj:`shuffle`, :py:obj:`permutation`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.choice.choice:29 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.choice.choice:30 of
msgid "Generate a uniform random sample from mt.arange(5) of size 3:"
msgstr "从 mt.arange(5) 中生成大小为 3 的均匀随机样本："

#: maxframe.tensor.random.choice.choice:38 of
msgid "Generate a non-uniform random sample from np.arange(5) of size 3:"
msgstr "从 np.arange(5) 中生成大小为 3 的非均匀随机样本："

#: maxframe.tensor.random.choice.choice:43 of
msgid ""
"Generate a uniform random sample from mt.arange(5) of size 3 without "
"replacement:"
msgstr "从 mt.arange(5) 中生成大小为 3 的无放回均匀随机样本："

#: maxframe.tensor.random.choice.choice:50 of
msgid ""
"Generate a non-uniform random sample from mt.arange(5) of size 3 without "
"replacement:"
msgstr "从 mt.arange(5) 中生成大小为 3 的无放回非均匀随机样本："

